briefdescription.para: Disable LWM2M object instance to stop providing sensor data. Sets unit to "" and all other values to 0. Function is thread safe, it schedules a job for serval. Execution may therefore be deferred.
Enables the LWM2M object instance to start providing sensor data. Function is thread safe, it schedules a job for serval. Execution may therefore be deferred.
Initialize LWM2M object instance. Must be called before any other function call.
